Welcome to our application.
On the left side, You can put to button 'Load by JS' and in left window will be added a list of users from the server( with the help 'XMLHttpRequest').
On the right side, You can put to button 'Load by Fetch',  and in  right window will be added a list of users from the server( with the help 'Fetch').
In input You can write some change and after put on button 'save' this changes will be added to server.

